episodes.title: Leaders of Secretive California Cult Charged with Murdering Members
episodes.description: The husband and wife leaders of “His Way Spirit Led Assemblies” were charged with murder along with two other members after the death of a 4-year-old boy and a 40-year-old man. Police say the murders happened more than 10 years apart, and there is another member who has been missing since 2019. Former members of the group who managed to escape, describe the bizarre and at times frightening atmosphere they lived in, for years. See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
